      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REDMAN JOHNNY (1) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in his solid 25.38 win at this track over 457m. Smart win two back and looks a key chance here. DEVENISH DEVIL (5) had been in super honest form hitting the frame three times on end before finishing fourth (22.11) at this track last time. Has a good record here including two wins. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Likely to play a prominent role. FLYAWAY JACK (2) has been out of the placings at his last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (16.76) in a Grade 5 at Q Straight. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. LAKEVIEW LIBBY (3) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
